answer: For the Quarterly Period Ended March 31, 2025, Meta Platforms, Inc. releases its 10-Q report, bearing the official title of "Quarterly Report on Form 10-Q." (Form 10-q, or more contemporary titles such as "Quarterly Report on Executive Compensation" if applicable, would be specific disclosures within it. The broader statutory disclosure would be its Form 10-K for annual reporting. It is the filing designed to provide quarterly financial information to shareholders.)
